flowchart LR
    P[Passenger App] --> GW[API Gateway]
    D[Driver App] --> GW

    GW --> AUTH[Auth Service]
    GW --> RIDE[Ride Service]
    GW --> DRIVER[Driver Service]
    GW --> TRACK[Tracking API]

    D --> LOC[Location Ingest Service]
    P --> LOC

    LOC --> KAFKA[(Kafka / Event Bus)]
    LOC --> GEO[(Redis GEO / In-memory Geo Index)]

    RIDE --> MATCH[Matching Service]
    MATCH --> GEO
    MATCH --> DRIVER
    MATCH --> OFFER[Offer Service]
    OFFER --> PUSH[Push / WebSocket Notifications]
    PUSH --> D
    PUSH --> P

    D --> OFFER
    OFFER --> RIDE

    RIDE --> TRIPDB[(Trips DB: PostgreSQL / Cassandra)]
    DRIVER --> DRIVERDB[(Drivers DB)]
    AUTH --> USERDB[(Users DB)]

    KAFKA --> TRACK
    TRACK --> ACTIVE[(Active Trips Cache)]
    TRACK --> P
    TRACK --> D

    RIDE --> HIST[History Service]
    HIST --> TRIPDB

    RIDE --> PAY[Payment Service]
    PAY --> PAYDB[(Payments DB)]

    KAFKA --> ANALYTICS[(Analytics / Cold Storage)]
